overview: QIC creates recognition and incentive programs that motivate people, inspire higher performance and deliver results. Offerings include channel sales incentives, customer incentive programs, employee recognition programs, safety incentive programs, wellness incentives, and years of service reward programs. Our incentive and recognition solutions are supported with a comprehensive menu of products and services that include incentive program design, a web-based program management platform, professionally designed presentation materials and rock-solid reward fulfillment.
